<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #eaf1fb;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 60, 136, 0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #1976d2;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px 20px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 24px 20px;
            color: #222b45;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .verification-code {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e3f0fd;
            color: #1976d2;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border: 1.5px solid #1976d2;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7a99;
            background-color: #eaf1fb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Verify Your Email, <%= name %>!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>We noticed you requested to resend your email verification code.</p>
            <p>Please use the code below to verify your email address and complete your registration:</p>
            <div class="verification-code">
                <%= verificationCode %>
            </div>
            <p>If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Our Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>